main event: Three separate objects appeared in the sky in Rolling, Wisconsin on June 5, 1966, observed by a civilian.
interesting points: The objects were observed for a duration of 5 minutes,The sighting occurred between 0900 and 0930 hours,The objects headed in a southeasterly direction, The description of the objects matched qualities similar to satellites, but seeing three objects in that location was unusual.
sighted object: three pale blue objects in the sky
